      "x": 90, "y": 805, "width": 480, "height": 80,
      "text": "🔌  Deployed Endpoint (stage 6)\n\nreads:  manifest.yaml  +  2-RecStore/\ndoes:   load record → run inference → return prediction\nnever:  touches stages 3-6 (they don't exist per-subject)",
