    {
      "type": "text", "id": "footer_body",
      "x": 100, "y": 970, "width": 1560, "height": 56,
      "text": "Steps 3 & 4 reuse the EXISTING fn_source + fn_record pipelines with a subject_id filter — no new code to maintain, no divergence between inference path and training path.\nIdempotent: re-running build() skips fresh folders (manifest.built_at check).  Reproducible: rm -rf Subject-*/ + re-build produces an equivalent folder (modulo timestamps).\nSource of truth stays global: _WorkSpace/0-RawDataStore/ + the build script.  Hand-edits to Subject-*/ are forbidden — they drift silently and break on re-build.",
      "originalText": "Steps 3 & 4 reuse the EXISTING fn_source + fn_record pipelines with a subject_id filter — no new code to maintain, no divergence between inference path and training path.\nIdempotent: re-running build() skips fresh folders (manifest.built_at check).  Reproducible: rm -rf Subject-*/ + re-build produces an equivalent folder (modulo timestamps).\nSource of truth stays global: _WorkSpace/0-RawDataStore/ + the build script.  Hand-edits to Subject-*/ are forbidden — they drift silently and break on re-build.",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
      "seed": 500005, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 500006,
      "isDeleted": false, "groupIds": [], "boundElements": null,
